imdb.plot outline: Even in the world of Entertainment, there's an hierarchy that separates the talent on offer on the African Continent. So it was inevitable that as the preeminent music channel on the continent Channel O had to release their own list. Channel O Top 10 Most is a a weekly 13-part series that countdowns the Top 10 Africans in a number of music categories. The show is hosted by Channel O VJs, Denrele and Jokate who brings their own unique brand of wit, zaniness and foolery but tempered with a seriousness that befits the countdown.
